Implement automated kernel tuning and optimization framework
- Added `tuner.py` for automated kernel tuning with support for TPU, GPU, and CPU. - Introduced `TuningConfig` and `TuningResult` data classes to manage tuning configurations and results. - Developed `KernelTuner` class to handle kernel tuning logic and profiling. - Created `AutotuneManager` for managing the autotuning process and storing tuning history. - Implemented CUDA-optimized kernels in `kernels.py` for matrix multiplication, flash attention, and layer normalization. - Added JIT compiler optimizations in `optimizer.py` for kernel fusion and profiling. - Developed TPU-optimized kernels in `kernels.py` for matrix multiplication, layer normalization, and attention mechanisms. - Established TPU mesh management in `mesh.py` for efficient distributed execution across TPU devices.
